{
  "stem": "5388.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were about six kilometers from the city, [POLISH], a village.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I used to go to school, walk six kilometers in the morning, and come back six kilometers, back morning and afternoon.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you're talking four, five miles walking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was a Yiddish school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was a Yiddish school with the general subject in Yiddish, but you also had Russian, of course.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had also German as a foreign language still.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, imagine for a Jewish school in those days to still have German as a foreign language.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But anyway, that was-- that's what it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I used to-- now-- and then we stayed there for a few months, and then we moved on the outskirts of the city.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Slonim, right, at Walenska 17 RA.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's where we lived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that was a-- a house away from the road.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the spring, it was always flooded.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Shara, the-- the lake, and the river used to go out of-- out of its bounds, and used to flood.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we used to go from the corner.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Somebody want to go home, you had to call the boats.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Somebody, if they saw you, they-- they would come quicker.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If not, you had to wait till a boat came to pick you up to go to the-- to this particular building.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't go anymore to any synagogues, and no more the Saturday services, and no more Maftirs, and no more haftarahs.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At that time I, was worried about being a Pioneer, to become a Pioneer, the Communist youth organization.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Pioneers, you know, Komsomol, and below that are Pioneers, and below that are the October children, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The youngsters.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
